---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../../components/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="LingMu UI/UX Prototype | Strategic Design">
	<main class="post-wrapper project-detail">
		<SectionHeader 
			tag="UI/UX / STRATEGIC DESIGN" 
			description="Interactive Prototype: Strategic sidebar navigation for immersive experience.">
			<h1 class="font-special text-5xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
				LingMu (灵沐)
			</h1>
		</SectionHeader>

		<section class="border-top" style="padding-top: 3rem;">
			<div class="content">
				<div class="project-intro-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
					<div>
						<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">Strategic Shift</h3>
						<p style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-200);">
							为了优化在大屏端的交互体验，我们将导航栏从底部移至<strong>左侧浮动区域</strong>。这一改动释放了底部视觉压力，使灵感记录过程更加沉浸且无遮挡。
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">Deployment</h3>
						<p style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-200);">
							原型通过 <strong>Vercel Edge Runtime</strong> 实时运行。左侧导航栏采用高斯模糊材质，确保在任何背景下都能保持清晰的层级关系。
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="pure-embed-viewport">
					<div class="clean-iframe-window">
						<div class="window-bar">
							<div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
							<span class="url">lingmu-app.vercel.app</span>
						</div>
						<div class="iframe-box">
							<iframe 
								src="https://lingmu-app.vercel.app" 
								style="border: none; width: 100%; height: 100%;" 
								allowfullscreen>
							</iframe>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-500); font-style: italic;">
					💡 提示：本窗口已启用左侧悬浮导航，你可以直接点击进行交互体验。
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<div style="height: 100px;"></div>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.project-detail {
		max-width: var(--max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 var(--pad-inner);
	}

	/* 1. 外层：负责撑开宽度和上下 breathing 间距 */
	.pure-embed-viewport {
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 20px 0;
	}

	/* 2. 容器：彻底删除手机比例锁，不再限制宽度，给予 80vh 的沉浸式高度 */
	.clean-iframe-window {
		width: 100%;
		height: 80vh; /* 撑开高度，确保侧边栏在视野正中 */
		min-height: 600px;
		background: #000;
		border-radius: 12px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}

	/* 3. 模拟系统顶部小条，增加高级感 */
	.window-bar {
		height: 36px;
		background: #1a1a1b;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 16px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
	.dots span { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #333; }
	.url { font-size: 10px; color: #666; font-family: monospace; }

	/* 4. Iframe：填满剩余空间 */
	.iframe-box {
		flex: 1;
		width: 100%;
		background: #fff; /* iframe 加载前的白底 */
	}

	/* 适配小屏幕 */
	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.clean-iframe-window {
			height: 70vh;
			min-height: 500px;
		}
	}
</style>
